1. What makes an undeniable pitch for an innovation project?
Solution : C. A clear description of the concept, an advanced prototype, a business case, and an implementation roadmap

2. Which components should you include in a Dream to Do framework?
Solution : A. A headline from the future, the next step in the transformation, business value, and metrics

3. What should you focus on to create and deliver a strong concept description as part of your Dream to Do sketch?
Solution : B. Make it clear-identify who the concept is for, what it is, what it does, and why it's needed
